---
title: Smothered Beef Burritos with Queso Blanco & Pico de Gallo
description: Turn burrito night into a full-out fiesta with this sauce smothered spin! First, you’ll stuff steamy flour tortillas with zesty lime rice and a spiced beef and tomato filling. But wrapping ‘em up is just the beginning! Next, they’re doused in enchilada sauce until basically drowning (in the best way), then finished with a fresh pico topping and a queso blanco drizzle. Elevating weeknight burritos to Mexican restaurant-level? The secret’s in the sauce!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/smothered-beef-burritos-7a52d5d2.jpg
